TestMethod.Description: This document cannot enumerate all possible safe local policy (the safest may be to simply reject all custom groups), but compatible clients that accept some custom groups from the server MUST do at least cursory checks on group size and may take other properties into consideration as well. [...]A compatible client that accepts FFDHE cipher suites using custom groups from non-compatible servers MUST reject any group with |dh_p| < 768 bits
